   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Remove the hydraulic fill port (screw type).</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Fill the hydraulic oil into the power pack tank.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>The oil level point should be positioned in the centre of gauge
              glass.</p>
            <p>
               <fig id="fig_ocp_23t_5gc">
                  <image href="media/image724a.png"
                         id="image_rcp_23t_5gc"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
      <div>
         <ol>
            <li>After turning the button to shifted position, hold the lever
located on the bottom.</li>
            <li>Put the lever into the power pack hydraulic jack.</li>
            <li>Move the lever up and down for manual tilting.</li>
         </ol>
      </div>
